\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
We start by listing three desirable properties that we want,
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
a function 
\begin_inset Formula $\det:\F^{n\times n}\to\F$
\end_inset

 to satisfy,
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
where 
